    <briefdescription>
<para>Processes incoming commands and dispatches them to appropriate services. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This application is responsible for:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Receiving raw byte streams via UART events.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Parsing and validating incoming command packets.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Publishing events for other services to handle. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
